=== Access ===
* From {{ill|lt=JR East|Q499071|WD=Q499071|lt=JR}} / {{ill|lt=Nagano Electric Railway|Q6958437|WD=Q6958437}}{{ill|lt=Nagano Station|Q374916|WD=Q374916}}, take the {{ill|lt=Alpico Kōtsū|Q4735443|WD=Q4735443}} ({{ill|lt=Kawanakajima Bus|Q11477633|WD=Q11477633}}) Route '''45''' and get off at “Morita Shrine-mae”

