=== Access ===
* From {{ill|lt=JR East|Q499071|WD=Q499071|lt=JR|1=East Japan Railway Company}} / {{ill|lt=Nagano Electric Railway|Q6958437|WD=Q6958437|1=Nagano Electric Railway}}{{ill|lt=Nagano Station|Q374916|WD=Q374916|1=Nagano Station}}, take the {{ill|lt=Alpico Kōtsū|Q4735443|WD=Q4735443|1=Alpico Kōtsū}} ({{ill|lt=Kawanakajima Bus|Q11477633|WD=Q11477633|1=Kawanakajima Bus}}) Route '''45''' and get off at “Morita Shrine-mae”

